            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1650971040868-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the pepper has softened, reduce the heat to medium</p><p>Add the<strong> orange sauce</strong> to the pan and cook for 1 min until the sauce has thickened</p><p>Once thickened, return the<strong> crispy meat-free chick'n </strong>to the pan and cook for 1 min further until the meat-free chick'n is coated in the sauce – this is your <strong>sticky orange meat-free chick'n</strong></p><p>Tip: If the sauce looks a little thick, add a splash of water!</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1650971044599-x200.jpg",
